Crispy Chicken Thighs with Sweet Potato Mash

45 min
$12.99
650 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy Optional

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Course

Tags:

Comfort FoodEasy MealChickenSweet Potato

Description

Juicy, crispy chicken thighs paired with creamy, sweet potato mash for a comforting meal.

Ingredients

  • chicken thighs: 4 pieces
  • sweet potatoes: 2 large
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: 1 teaspoon
  • black pepper: 1 teaspoon
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • butter: 2 tablespoons
  • milk: 1/4 cup
